our literacy conference today

00:00:33.550 --> 00:00:38.260
here on reading promotion in the
battle to keep people reading.

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:41.290
It's great to see all of you
thanks to our participants

00:00:41.290 --> 00:00:43.250
as well as our attendees.

