who has organized this event.

00:01:30.970 --> 00:01:32.270
I like the title.

00:01:32.270 --> 00:01:35.280
I don't know who came up with
that but reading promotion

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:36.930
in the battle to
keep people reading,

00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:39.250
those of us who worked a
lot with Dr. Billington

00:01:39.250 --> 00:01:44.580
over the years, he always
talked about battle plans.

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:47.910
I don't know whether-- I haven't
worked enough with Dr. Hayden,

00:01:47.910 --> 00:01:49.520
you know, whether
she uses that phrase,

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:52.250
but Dr. Billington would always
say we need a battle plan

00:01:52.250 --> 00:01:53.870
for this and a battle
plan for that.

00:01:53.870 --> 00:01:57.010
So if it's a battle to
keep people reading,

00:01:57.010 --> 00:02:01.030
one of the things I would think
would be possibly emerging

00:02:01.030 --> 00:02:04.660
from this meeting would be
something like a battle plan

00:02:04.660 --> 00:02:07.570
or at least elements that
would go into a battle plan.

00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:11.690
So it should be a
very interesting day.

