And one quick little
story, Annie Ward,

00:15:00.410 --> 00:15:04.190
assistant superintendent of
Mamaroneck School District,

00:15:04.190 --> 00:15:11.100
which is just north of New
York City is doing something

00:15:11.100 --> 00:15:12.400
so fabulous.

00:15:12.400 --> 00:15:14.340
I just have to tell
real quickly.

00:15:14.340 --> 00:15:21.660
How many of you are
familiar with Stitch Fix?

00:15:21.660 --> 00:15:24.330
Does anyone in here heard that?

00:15:24.330 --> 00:15:30.180
You fill out a profile of
the kinds of clothes you

00:15:30.180 --> 00:15:34.450
like to read and then they put
together a custom box for you.

00:15:34.450 --> 00:15:39.130
Well, in Mamaroneck district,
the kids are filling out list

00:15:39.130 --> 00:15:46.030
of the kinds of books they
like to read and working

