00:51:28.520 --> 00:51:33.540
A couple of things about what it
means to be a voracious reader.

00:51:33.540 --> 00:51:38.330
And I suspect most of the people
in the room are like this.

00:51:38.330 --> 00:51:40.480
She didn't just pick
