00:51:49.510 --> 00:51:52.000
Somebody rigged up
something that she--

00:51:52.000 --> 00:51:54.320
she used to swim
laps every morning.

00:51:54.320 --> 00:51:56.840
Actually she did
that her whole life.

00:51:56.840 --> 00:51:58.570
Somebody rigged up
something for her when she was

00:51:58.570 --> 00:52:03.350
in the White House that she
could read while she was doing

00:52:03.350 --> 00:52:11.190
laps and somehow who knows, it
was a much less partisan time

00:52:11.190 --> 00:52:14.100
so nobody blamed it
