01:03:15.140 --> 01:03:16.600
What are you going
to do about that?

01:03:16.600 --> 01:03:18.970
So we had to find the
money to make sure

01:03:18.970 --> 01:03:22.020
that we could make sure those
kids got their books signed they

01:03:22.020 --> 01:03:25.470
