for author visits.

01:03:57.660 --> 01:04:01.440
So that's something that we
do with them, so we make sure

01:04:01.440 --> 01:04:07.560
that we take our authors
to visit those schools.

01:04:07.560 --> 01:04:09.810
Wes Moore who was a prominent,

01:04:09.810 --> 01:04:13.310
was a prominent Baltimorean I
think he's gone to New York now

01:04:13.310 --> 01:04:18.180
but every year he would
come to the Pratt library

01:04:18.180 --> 01:04:21.240
