01:07:05.030 --> 01:07:09.150
Libraries Without Borders is
a nonprofit that's focusing

01:07:09.150 --> 01:07:12.260
on expanding access to
information particularly

01:07:12.260 --> 01:07:15.090
in the most vulnerable
communities.

01:07:15.090 --> 01:07:19.170
