with you about this,

01:10:24.740 --> 01:10:28.500
how can the Ideas Box
potentially support your efforts

01:10:28.500 --> 01:10:31.680
in these tough contexts.

01:10:31.680 --> 01:10:34.340
But what I really want to
talk with you about today

