01:22:25.520 --> 01:22:27.830
which we call it
reading program,

01:22:27.830 --> 01:22:29.300
reading awareness program.

01:22:29.300 --> 01:22:33.000
Everybody wins a whole bunch
of programs of that ilk.

01:22:33.000 --> 01:22:39.320
Again, out of the box-- a
bit and Rachel, I think,

01:22:39.320 --> 01:22:41.260
[inaudible] representing
one organization.

01:22:41.260 --> 01:22:44.510
She'll speak for her
broad experience.

