needs help and we're doing a lot

01:33:47.020 --> 01:33:50.950
of the things that we all know
are right but we can learn

01:33:50.950 --> 01:33:52.540
from each other and
I really appreciate

01:33:52.540 --> 01:33:55.370
that we're given the opportunity
to talk to each other and talk

01:33:55.370 --> 01:34:00.140
about our mistakes because those
are the things we want to avoid.

