02:03:00.410 --> 02:03:02.930
and then develop their
own podcast to share

02:03:02.930 --> 02:03:06.350
that information with other
schools, other students,

02:03:06.350 --> 02:03:10.920
other communities,
which was a lot of fun.

02:03:12.280 --> 02:03:13.580
&gt;&gt; Benita Somerfield: OK.

