02:03:30.680 --> 02:03:35.100
And also encourage people
to read in whatever way

02:03:35.100 --> 02:03:37.690
who might not otherwise
be doing that.

02:03:37.690 --> 02:03:41.990
Now for myself I love nothing
more than as an individual

02:03:41.990 --> 02:03:44.360
and private person curling
up with a good book.

02:03:44.360 --> 02:03:47.340
But I'm also-- I also
really enjoy a book club.

02:03:47.340 --> 02:03:52.200
